257
0:10:38.26,000 --> 0:10:4,000
And many of the tropical flowers are red,

258
0:10:40.26,000 --> 0:10:42,000
and that's because butterflies and birds

259
0:10:42.26,000 --> 0:10:44,000
see similarly to us, we think,

260
0:10:44.26,000 --> 0:10:47,000
